parameters:
Well, you see... First, I'll graduate and receive a noble title.
Then, I'll marry an upper-class noble and live a life of luxury.
That's the goal, right?
No way...! It's impossible for you, right...? Hehe.
Haa...!? Well, you won't know until you try it...!

What about Lunaroa? She seems like she'll go even higher, right?
Skipping over upper-class and going straight to privilege or
something...

\SE[3]Hmm... Well, I'm not really from that kind of background...
\SE[6]I was born into an ordinary family too...
I think your parents and teachers would be really happy though.

\SE[0] (I wonder if Laura would be happy? Like, Wow, Lunaroa,
you're amazing! or something...?)

\SE[6](No, maybe we'll be like, We have no idea! together.
\SE[20]It's more likely to be that way.)
\SE[0] (I wonder if Laura is doing well...)

\SE[2]Excuse me, but that's my seat. \SE[3]May I take your
belongings?

That girl is a little scary, right? Just because she sat on the
chair for a bit.
Hey, she's always in a bad mood, you know.
